parameters: The final battle, where we bet our dreams, begins!
The ball slowly falls into just the right position.

Because the ball that everyone thought was out rode the wind
and came in,...

Even Akane, who has excellent motor skills, was delayed in
dealing with it.

Hikaru caught the ball just barely, but naturally, that kind
of ball didn't have any power and it fell in front of
Hikaru without the strength to make an effective hit.

Ussha! I wonder if there's ever been a spike that hit at the
speed of light?

And saying that, they jumped to spike and tossed it
towards Kanae.
Saying that, they jump and spike it back!

Like a salmon swimming against the current, Kanae jumps as
if she were in a painting.

Soon, a light and lively sound of pan! echoed on the sandy
beach.

The spike that pierces through the gap between Akane and
Renka!

I can't believe we won, even though Akane was our
opponent!

Kanade's shadow overlapped with me, who had extended onto the
sandy beach after giving it my all in a powerful toss.

Then, they squatted down next to me and started stroking my
head with their small hands.

I mischievously turned my body around to match the
timing of their stroking, and licked Kanae's hand.
This guy! He just licked me!
Because we were playing beach volleyball until just now.
Did you touch my head with those hands?

What's this? If the super beautiful Kanae-sama is going to
stroke your head, you shouldn't feel shy.
Hehe, princess? That sounds nice. Tell me more.

It's fine to laugh and make noise, but let's start the next
round soon.

The Hikaru team defeated a formidable enemy and advanced
to victory!
...However, this pair never won the championship.

The Hikaru team, who gave their all in a fierce battle
against the Akane team, surprisingly suffered a
crushing defeat in the following championship match.
